# Game - Pivot or Die

educational game about pivoting in the Technological disruptions, to show people that tech changes create prosperity and the AI will enrich us and not "take all our jobs" but instead although killing some jobs and industries it creates new one.

TECHNOLOGY is always a net job creator.

created with claude

## How to play

1. scroll down and click "Start your Journey"
2. each era read prologue, answer why industry is closing, and choose a pivot.
3. [play it here](https://bresleveloper.github.io/Game-PivotOrDie/)




